Description:
NEW YEAR. NEW YOU. NEW PROPERTY.
"We're only a few days into the new year and this is already 2020's best buy."
Massive block in the heart of Lang Lang with a four bedroom home positioned strategically at the front of the block.
Spanning 735sqm (approx) with rear access it makes this property an ideal future subdivision property (STCA).
While the house needs some love, the floor plan is quite appealing.
- Four bedrooms;
- Separate living and dining zones;
- Heating and cooling;
- Alfresco;
- Shed.
Ray White prides itself on being as accurate as possible however anyone considering purchasing the property should undertake their own due diligence to confirm the above.
